    Description

    Service class for managing interview experiences.

    Represents the type of employment being offered or applied for.

    JWT Authentication Filter that processes JWT tokens in the Authorization header.
    JwtAuthenticationResponse
    Data Transfer Object representing the response for JWT authentication.
    JwtTokenProvider
    Component responsible for JWT token generation, validation, and parsing.

    Data Transfer Object representing a user login request.

    ResourceNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a requested resource is not found in the system.

    SignUpRequest

    UserService
